872
00:39:06,683 --> 00:39:07,834
The dogs are getting confused.

873
00:39:09,117 --> 00:39:10,222
You think he wants his land back?

874
00:39:10,401 --> 00:39:11,797
What in the hell is going on here?

875
00:39:11,848 --> 00:39:12,469
Mr. Hammond...

876
00:39:12,520 --> 00:39:13,295
